      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "1: Stakeholder Mapping and Resource Mapping in Kathmandu and province and collect DRRM resource data collection and well documentation of the resources.2: A-PAD platform Coordination MTG (KTM) and province to establish national and provincial level A-PAD multi-sectorial platform.3: Organize International Symposium in Kathmandu and province4 : Print PR materials5: Increased knowledge and skills of disaster-prone communities on DRRM7: Trained Vols from community and mobilized them for DRRM8: Strengthen local governments mechanism for effective DRRM through capacity building and  Reviewed/update the existing DRR policies, acts, strategies and plans9: Well-equipped LEOC and DEOC with basic DIMS equipment"
